      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of the S54-powered legend. The naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six delivers linear power through six individual throttle bodies, paired with a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen features a reinforced subframe and a recently overhauled dual-VANOS system, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency and variable valve timing precision. The factory limited-slip differential provides exceptional mechanical grip, while the suspension geometry remains tight and factory-spec. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this vehicle displays zero aesthetic or mechanical degradation, representing a turn-key investment for the serious purist.",
